{"id":"built-in-instructions2.html","dependencies":[],"generated":{"html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"en\">\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <title>条件渲染</title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n    <div id=\"app\">\r\n        v-if:后接等号，等号内容必须是布尔值<br>\r\n        <p v-if=\"6<3\">{{apple}}</p>\r\n        <p v-else-if=\"9>5\">{{peach}}</p>\r\n        <p v-else=\"\">{{pear}}</p>\r\n        <hr>\r\n        v-if实例:<br>\r\n        点击按钮实现用户名输入框和密码输入框的切换\r\n        <div v-if=\"type==='name'\">\r\n            用户名：<input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"请输入用户名\" key=\"name\">   \r\n        </div>\r\n        <div v-else=\"\">\r\n            密码:<input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"请输入密码\" key=\"psw\">  \r\n        </div>\r\n        <button @click=\"toggleType\">切换</button>\r\n        <hr>\r\n        v-if的弊端，Vue在渲染元素时，处于效率的考虑，会尽可能地复用已有的元素而非重新渲染，\r\n        只会渲染改变的元素 \r\n        解决方法：提供key值可以决定是否复用该元素(key是唯一的)\r\n        <hr>\r\n        v-show用法： 显现与否取决于他的布尔值\r\n        <p v-show=\"9>a\">我被渲染了</p>\r\n        <hr>\r\n        v-if与v-show的比较：\r\n        v-if 实时渲染，页面显示就会渲染，不显示，就被移除\r\n        v-show 一次渲染 后面显示与否只是改变display的值\r\n\r\n\r\n    </div>    \r\n\r\n\r\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/vue@2/dist/vue.js\"></script>\r\n    <script>\r\n        var app=new Vue({\r\n            el:\"#app\",\r\n            data:{\r\n                apple:'apple',\r\n                pear:'pear',\r\n                peach:'peach',\r\n                type:'name',\r\n                a:3\r\n            },\r\n            methods:{\r\n                toggleType:function(){\r\n                    this.type=(this.type==='name' ? 'password' : 'name')\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n        })\r\n    </script>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>"},"hash":"0693347a10973191a9e81b4efc80eea6","cacheData":{}}